name: Darth Vader, Dark Lord Of The Sith
Lore: 'Formerly Anakin Skywalker, Jedi Knight. Became Darth Vader. Ordered by Emperor Palpatine to deal with Luke Skywallker, but bargained for his son''s life instead.',
Text: 'Adds 3 to power of anything he pilots. When in a battle, may target one opponent''s character present. Draw destiny. Target ''choked'' (lost) if destiny > ability. Immune to attrition < 5.',
